{"data":{"allPostTitles":{"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/accessibility/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/getting-started/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/mode-and-value/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/accessibility/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/format/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/getting-started/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/limits/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/orientation/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/ticks/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/tooltip/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/types/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/how-to/customize-color-picker/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/how-to/disable-color-picker/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/how-to/hide-control-buttons/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/how-to/render-palette-alone/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}}]},"postBySlug":{"html":"<h1 id=\"accessibility\"><a href=\"#accessibility\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Accessibility</h1>\n<p>The Slider is characterized with complete ARIA Accessibility support that helps to access by on-screen readers and other assistive technology devices. This control is designed with the reference of guidelines document given in the <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria-practices/#slider\">WAI ARAI Accessibility Practices</a>.</p>\n<p>The Slider control uses the Slider role and the following ARIA properties for its element based on the state.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><strong>Properties</strong></th>\n<th><strong>Functionalities</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">aria-valuenow</code></td>\n<td>It Indicates the current value of the slider.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">aria-valuetext</code></td>\n<td>Returns the current text of the slider.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">aria-valuemin</code></td>\n<td>It Indicates the Minimum value of the slider.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">aria-valuemax</code></td>\n<td>It Indicates the Maximum value of the slider.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">aria-orientation</code></td>\n<td>It Indicates the Slider Orientation.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">aria-label</code></td>\n<td>Slider left and right button label text (increment and decrement).</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">aria-labelledby</code></td>\n<td>It indicates the name of the Slider.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"keyboard-interaction\"><a href=\"#keyboard-interaction\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Keyboard interaction</h2>\n<p>The Keyboard interaction of the Slider control is designed based on the <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria-practices/#slider\">WAI-ARIA Practices</a> described for Slider. Users can use the following shortcut keys to interact with the Slider.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><strong>Keyboard shortcuts</strong></th>\n<th><strong>Actions</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><kbd>Right Arrow</kbd> <kbd>Up Arrow</kbd></td>\n<td>Increase the Slider value.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><kbd>Left Arrow</kbd> <kbd>Down Arrow</kbd></td>\n<td>Decrease the Slider value.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><kbd>Home</kbd></td>\n<td>Moves to the start value (for Range Slider when the second thumb is focused and the Home key is pressed, it moves to the first thumb value).</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><kbd>End</kbd></td>\n<td>Moves to the end value (for Range Slider when the first thumb is focused and the End key is pressed, it moves to the second thumb value).</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><kbd>Page Up</kbd></td>\n<td>Increases the Slider by <code class=\"language-text\">LargeStep</code> value.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><kbd>Page Down</kbd></td>\n<td>Decreases the Slider by <code class=\"language-text\">LargeStep</code> value.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","timeToRead":2,"excerpt":"Accessibility The Slider is characterized with complete ARIA Accessibility support that helps to access by on-screen readers and otherâ€¦","fields":{"slug":"/slider/accessibility/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/slider/accessibility/","previous":{"html":"<h1 id=\"formatting\"><a href=\"#formatting\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Formatting</h1>\n<p>The <code class=\"language-text\">Format</code> feature used to customize the units of Slider values to desired format. The formatted values will also be applied to the ARIA attributes of the slider. There are two ways of achieving formatting in slider.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Use the <code class=\"language-text\">Format</code> API of slider which utilizes our Internationalization to format values.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csharp\"><pre class=\"language-csharp\"><code class=\"language-csharp\">@<span class=\"token keyword\">using</span> Syncfusion<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>EJ2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Blazor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Inputs\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">EjsSlider</span> Value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"30\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">SliderTooltipData</span> IsVisible<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"true\"</span> ShowOn<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"TooltipShowOn.Always\"</span> Format<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"C2\"</span> Placement<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"TooltipPlacement.Before\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>SliderTooltipData<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">SliderTicksData</span> Placement<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Placement.Before\"</span> Format<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"C2\"</span> ShowSmallTicks<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"true\"</span> LargeStep<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"20\"</span> SmallStep<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"10\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>SliderTicksData<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>EjsSlider<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"/production/blazor/documentation/slider/images/slider-format.gif\" alt=\"Blazor - Slider - Format\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"using-format-api\"><a href=\"#using-format-api\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Using format API</h2>\n<p>Slider provides different predefined formatting styles like Numeric (N), Percentage (P), Currency (C) and # specifiers. In this below example we have formatted the ticks and tooltip values into percentage.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csharp\"><pre class=\"language-csharp\"><code class=\"language-csharp\">@<span class=\"token keyword\">using</span> Syncfusion<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>EJ2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Blazor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Inputs\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">EjsSlider</span> Min<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"1\"</span> Max<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"10\"</span> Value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"3\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">SliderTicksData</span> Placement<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Placement.After\"</span> Format<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"P0\"</span> ShowSmallTicks<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"true\"</span> LargeStep<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"2\"</span> SmallStep<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"1\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>SliderTicksData<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">SliderTooltipData</span> IsVisible<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"true\"</span> ShowOn<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"TooltipShowOn.Always\"</span> Format<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"P0\"</span> Placement<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"TooltipPlacement.Before\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>SliderTooltipData<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>EjsSlider<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"/production/blazor/documentation/slider/images/slider-format-api.gif\" alt=\"Blazor - Slider - Format API\"></p>","id":"6cabf3c7-0e93-5c45-86d5-c30944990c67","fields":{"slug":"/slider/format/","parentPath":"slider","childPath":"format","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4","header":"","breadCrumb":"Slider/Formatting","isReleaseNotes":false,"title":"Formatting in Blazor [Preview] Slider component - Syncfusion","description":"Checkout and learn about Formatting in Blazor [Preview] Slider component of Syncfusion Essential JS 2, and more details.","platform":"Blazor [Preview]","isRobots":true}},"next":{"html":"<h1 id=\"mode-and-value\"><a href=\"#mode-and-value\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Mode and Value</h1>\n<h2 id=\"rendering-palette-at-initial-load\"><a href=\"#rendering-palette-at-initial-load\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Rendering palette at initial load</h2>\n<p>By default, the <code class=\"language-text\">Picker</code> area will be rendered at initial load. To render the Palette area while opening the ColorPicker pop-up, specify the <a href=\"https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-blazor/Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor~Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Inputs.EjsColorPicker~Mode.html\"><code class=\"language-text\">mode</code></a> property as <code class=\"language-text\">Palette</code>.</p>\n<p>In the following sample, it will render the <code class=\"language-text\">Palette</code> at initial load.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"razor\"><pre class=\"language-razor\"><code class=\"language-razor\">&lt;div class=&quot;wrapper&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;h4&gt;Choose a color&lt;/h4&gt;\n    &lt;EjsColorPicker ID=&#39;element&#39; Mode=&quot;ColorPickerMode.Palette&quot;&gt;&lt;/EjsColorPicker&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;style&gt;\n.wrapper {\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    width: 300px;\n    text-align: center;\n}\n&lt;/style&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p>Output be like\n<img src=\"/production/blazor/documentation/color-picker/images/palette.png\" alt=\"color-picker\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"color-value\"><a href=\"#color-value\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Color value</h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-blazor/Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor~Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Inputs.EjsColorPicker~Value.html\"><code class=\"language-text\">value</code></a> property can be used to specify the color value to the ColorPicker. It supports either <code class=\"language-text\">three</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">six</code> digit hex codes. To include <code class=\"language-text\">opacity</code>, set the color value as <code class=\"language-text\">four</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">eight</code> digit hex code.</p>\n<p>In the following sample, the color value sets as <code class=\"language-text\">four</code> digit hex code, the last digit represents the <code class=\"language-text\">opacity</code> value.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"razor\"><pre class=\"language-razor\"><code class=\"language-razor\">&lt;div class=&quot;wrapper&quot;&gt;\n     &lt;h4&gt;Choose a color&lt;/h4&gt;\n     &lt;EjsColorPicker ID=&#39;element&#39;Value=&quot;035a&quot; ModeSwitcher=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;/EjsColorPicker&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;style&gt;\n.wrapper {\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    width: 300px;\n    text-align: center;\n    }\n&lt;/style&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p>Output be like\n<img src=\"/production/blazor/documentation/color-picker/images/color-value.png\" alt=\"color-picker\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-blazor/Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor~Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Inputs.EjsColorPicker~Value.html\"><code class=\"language-text\">value</code></a> property\nsupports hex code with or without <code class=\"language-text\">#</code> prefix.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>","id":"61abd35a-e727-5993-b62f-35b32ef70fc4","fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/mode-and-value/","parentPath":"color-picker","childPath":"mode-and-value","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4","header":"<div id=\"doc-right-toc\"><span>Contents</span>\n<ul>\n  <li class=\"doc-anchor-h2\"><a href=\"#rendering-palette-at-initial-load\">Rendering palette at initial load</a></li>\n  <li class=\"doc-anchor-h2\"><a href=\"#color-value\">Color value</a></li>\n</ul></div>","breadCrumb":"ColorPicker/Mode and Value","isReleaseNotes":false,"title":"Mode and Value in Blazor [Preview] ColorPicker component - Syncfusion","description":"Checkout and learn about Mode and Value in Blazor [Preview] ColorPicker component of Syncfusion Essential JS 2, and more details.","platform":"Blazor [Preview]","isRobots":true}},"gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4","header":"","breadCrumb":"Slider/Accessibility","isReleaseNotes":false,"title":"Accessibility in Blazor [Preview] Slider component - Syncfusion","description":"Checkout and learn about Accessibility in Blazor [Preview] Slider component of Syncfusion Essential JS 2, and more details.","platform":"Blazor [Preview]","isRobots":true}}